Rocaloid is a vocal synthesis engine which aims to enable Hatsune Miku to sing in Chinese (and maybe other languages).
The synthesis engine, CVE, currently uses time-domain algorism like PSOLA. Sleepwalking called it "TDPSM" (Time Domain Pitch Synchronize and Mix).
For more information about our project, please visit http://bbs.ivocaloid.com/forum-138-1.html.
